rComments: No grades were given for any assignments all semester, but he expected you to have work done every week and some progress to show. Did not record lectures or post one thing on Brightspace. We all had to wait to get our final grade to know if we even passed the class. I taught myself the course content on Youtube. No structure at all, just terrible.

Justin is soo passionate about photography and it shows. He is always willing to talk to students after class about problems they are having, or artists they are interested in and has been known to come in on days when there is no class to help students with projects. He is extremely helpful and knowledgable.
Very helpful man; has been known to stay a couple hours after each class to help his students. Funny, friendly, a great choice for anyone interested in photo!
A dedicated and talented prof who know EVERYTHING about photography.  This man is awesome.  He will readily meet you outside of class and help you troubleshoot anything.  Great class.
